  "description": "<p><strong>Temp Student Care</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><p>- Ushering of students</p><p>- Look after students during break time</p><p>- Require to walk around the school when the lesson is on-going<br /><br />- Assist in paperwork such as data entry, photocopy and etc.</p><p>- Other ad hoc duties as assigned by in-charge</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Other information:</strong></p><p>- Working hours: Monday to Friday (8.30am to 5.30pm)</p><p>- Salary: $12 per hour</p><p>- Location: Bukit Timah (Walking distance from Beauty World MRT)</p><p>- Able to commit for at least 1 to 3 months or long term.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Interested candidate, please send in your resume to recruit@dismanpower.com.sg and state \"Temp Student Care - BT\" as the subject.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>DIS Manpower Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No.: 08C3226</p><p>Sng Wei Lin</p><p>Reg No.: R1101806</p>",
